To many, the 911 is already a work of art. @nelsonmakamo, one of South Africa’s leading artists, certainly thinks so. But when he took delivery of his new 911 Carrera, he felt compelled to go one step further by giving his car a brightly-coloured twist in Nelson’s inimitable style. The results serve as a moving tribute to the mother who inspired him and a dazzling example of his – and his homeland’s – unique artistic talent.
